# Frontend FSD

```
app/       → providers, router, global styles
pages/     → route entry, thin composition
widgets/   → layout shell, dashboard blocks
features/  → modals, filters, actions (customer-modal, ticket-form)
entities/  → customer/api.ts, customer/types.ts
shared/ui/ → Modal, Pagination, DataTable, Input, Button
shared/api/→ http client, parseMeta
```

## Modal pattern
```tsx
// features/customer-modal/ui/CustomerModal.tsx
// Uses shared/ui/Modal – fixed overlay, z-index 1000
<Modal open={open} onClose={onClose} title="Thêm khách hàng">
  <CustomerForm onSuccess={onClose} />
</Modal>
```

## Pagination
- Use `usePaginatedQuery(entityApi.list, filters)` hook in feature layer.
- Page component only: `<CustomerPage />` renders `<CustomerTable />` + `<CustomerModal />`.

## Styling
- CSS variables in `app/styles/variables.css`.
- No inline styles except dynamic values.
